2026-07-08T09:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],"yoga","wellness","fitness",false,"/images/flow-1.png","Beginning a yoga practice can feel overwhelming, but this 7-day program breaks it down into manageable daily sessions.\n\n![Daily Flow](/images/flow-1.png)\n\n## Day 1: Breathing & Centering\nStart with pranayama (breathing exercises) and basic meditation.\n\n## Day 2: Standing Poses\nFocus on Mountain Pose, Warrior I, and Downward-Facing Dog.\n\n## Day 3-7: Progressive Practice\nEach day builds on the previous, introducing new poses and deeper stretches.\n\nConsistency is more important than perfection. Start today!\n\n![Daily Flow](/images/flow-2.png)","src/content/blog/yoga-beginners-7-day.md","7dd4a3b301f7c4b3",{"html":27,"metadata":28},"\u003Cp>Beginning a yoga practice can feel overwhelming, but this 7-day program breaks it down into manageable daily sessions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/flow-1.png\" alt=\"Daily Flow\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"day-1-breathing--centering\">Day 1: Breathing &#x26; Centering\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Start with pranayama (breathing exercises) and basic meditation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"day-2-standing-poses\">Day 2: Standing Poses\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Focus on Mountain Pose, Warrior I, and Downward-Facing Dog.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"day-3-7-progressive-practice\">Day 3-7: Progressive Practice\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Each day builds on the previous, introducing new poses and deeper stretches.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Consistency is more important than perfection. Start today!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/flow-2.png\" alt=\"Daily Flow\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":29,"localImagePaths":40,"remoteImagePaths":41,"frontmatter":42,"imagePaths":45},[30,34,37],{"depth":31,"slug":32,"text":33},2,"day-1-breathing--centering","Day 1: Breathing & Centering",{"depth":31,"slug":35,"text":36},"day-2-standing-poses","Day 2: Standing Poses",{"depth":31,"slug":38,"text":39},"day-3-7-progressive-practice","Day 3-7: Progressive Practice",[],[],{"title":14